    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>On Tape &lt;&lt; Rewind</strong> is a psychological horror game where you solve a mystery through cassette tapes.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You arrive at Fred Karlsen's isolated cabin. The physicist has vanished, leaving behind scattered tapes and one fragmented message. His voice crackles through static, unravelling and afraid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The message is a warning. Something is out there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/2fc859fe5ab810b56e8d56bc36325dc7.poster.avif?t=1769790503\" width=1170 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/2fc859fe5ab810b56e8d56bc36325dc7.webm?t=1769790503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/2fc859fe5ab810b56e8d56bc36325dc7.mp4?t=1769790503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play back tapes on a dusty cassette recorder. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search the cabin for clues. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate audio frequencies to reveal hidden messages. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each discovery points you toward the next tape.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each recording is a piece of the puzzle. Cold War research logs. An old news broadcast. Medical journals. Experimental music. Static noise. And amidst everything - an unfinished letter to an old friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/e9e2b3e00389031727454da73e4771a4.poster.avif?t=1769790503\" width=1170 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/e9e2b3e00389031727454da73e4771a4.webm?t=1769790503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/e9e2b3e00389031727454da73e4771a4.mp4?t=1769790503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tape by tape, the truth emerges. You uncover Fred's growing fear and obsession with something he found in the recordings - something that listened back. You follow the same trail, rewinding through the fragments of his life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What happened to Fred? Why was he alone out here? And what is waiting in the static?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/5ebce6052dff0306e845ffd77509014e.poster.avif?t=1769790503\" width=1170 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/5ebce6052dff0306e845ffd77509014e.webm?t=1769790503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316280/extras/5ebce6052dff0306e845ffd77509014e.mp4?t=1769790503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
